stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OPEN
    OPEN --> CLAIMED: TASK_CLAIM (lease)
    CLAIMED --> DONE_SPLIT: expand L levels
    CLAIMED --> DONE_EXHAUSTED: DFS exhausted
    CLAIMED --> SOLVED: solution found (first wins)
    CLAIMED --> OPEN: lease expired (crash)
    OPEN --> DEAD: DEAD_END prune
    CLAIMED --> DEAD: DEAD_END prune
    DONE_SPLIT --> DONE_EXHAUSTED: all children exhausted
    DONE_EXHAUSTED --> [*]: if root then UNSOLVABLE
    SOLVED --> [*]
